metadata.description: I am sharing with you all, a little bit of me and my family. These are the hands of me and my twins. One of my twins was diagnosed at birth with Dwarfism. I am spreading awareness so that we know more about dwarfism and  we can all live in peace with one another & make this world a better place for future generations to come.
metadata.name: Dwarfism Awareness (October) Mola Art
